data.content:
Động từ
làm tan băng, làm tan sương giá
defrost the car windscreen
làm tan sương giá ở kính chắn gió xe hơi
[làm cho] hết đông lạnh
a frozen chicken should be allowed to defrost completely before cooking
gà đông lạnh phải để cho hoàn toàn hết đông lạnh rồi mới nấu nướng

verb
-frosts; -frosted; -frosting
to warm something that is frozen until it is no longer frozen [+ obj]
You can defrost the soup in the microwave. [no obj]
He took some fish out of the freezer to defrost [=thaw] in the fridge. - sometimes used figuratively
It took a while for her to defrost [=to stop being unfriendly] and open up to us.
to melt ice that has built up on the inside of a freezer or refrigerator [+ obj]
defrost the freezer [no obj]
Has the refrigerator defrosted yet?
[+ obj] :to melt ice on a car's windows by using heat
defrost the windshield - compare defog, deice
